oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Young couple
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Shows an unidentified young couple. The young man is seated; the woman stands behind him, wearing a dress with puffed sleeves, gloves, and a large picture hat with ostrich feathers. Photographed for J. I. Marshall.
